methods.appendRowSequence:
Appends a RowSequence to this builder.

:param rowSequence: (io.deephaven.engine.rowset.RowSequence) - The RowSequence to append
methods.appendRowSequenceWithOffset:
Appends a RowSequence shifted by the provided offset to this builder.

:param rowSequence: (io.deephaven.engine.rowset.RowSequence) - The RowSequence to append
:param shiftAmount: (long) - An offset to apply to every range in the RowSet

text: RowSetBuilderRandom implementation that uses an OrderedLongSetBuilderSequential internally.
